article_id:1884,category_name:News,title_name:Installment #30 of Notte's Super Rad Plot Synopsis Is Here!,image_path:,message:<div>Installment #30 of Notte&#39;s Super Rad Plot Synopsis, a four-panel comic series in which players can quickly become familiar with the main beats of Dragalia Lost&#39;s plot, is now available both in-game and on the official website.</div><div><br></div><div>■To read in-game</div><div>On the Home screen, tap the Menu (book) button on the top right of the screen, then tap on Notte&#39;s Super Rad Plot Synopsis.</div><div><br></div><div>■To read on the official website</div><div>On the main page of the official website, scroll down until you see the Notte&#39;s Super Rad Plot Synopsis banner, then click it.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1611554400,update_time1608886883